i.    After creating the Instance properly. Copy the IPv4 address and paste into the Google browser.
ii.   If We will get  "This site canâ€™t be reached" then come back to instance dashboard.
iii.  Top of the Dashboard There is a button with the name of CONNECT. Click on that.
iv.   Connect to Instance page - Click CONNECT once again.
