2.    

i. Once Console is opened after clicking on CONNECT then proceed with the below commands:-

   For check the status of server that it's running or not :- sudo systemctl status httpd

     sudo yum install httpd 
     sudo systemctl start httpd
     sudo systemctl enable httpd
     sudo su
     echo "Hello world" > /var/www/html/index.html
     systemctl restart httpd



